cat << EOF
tako is a command language and shell for GNU/Linux.
tako is not "sh"-compatible, but rather is designed to provide an intuitive
interface for common shell operations (to reduce time spent looking up how to
do things in Bash/sed/awk).
A short list of nice features:
  Typed variables
  Rich Python ecosystem directly from the shell
  "Less weird" syntax for inline commands and scripts
  Simple interactive interface, small codebase, low CPU usage.
EOF
